Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}我回來了 你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}今天也很忙 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}我也剛回來沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}再等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}我去沖個澡 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}今天住這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}今天丟廚餘啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}你最近有看到他太太嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}聽說太太外遇離婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}看起來像正常人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}外遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}你是不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}好吃嗎 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}頭有點昏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}叫救護車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}送你到家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}他家就住那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}鑰匙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}在包包裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}可能是貧血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}那我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}要喝點水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}今天身體不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}到住家附近就頭昏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}水我放這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}我是跑這附近的業務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}今天身體不舒服早退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}回到住家附近頭很昏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}是鄰居扶我回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}是不是回個禮比較好
