Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}之前真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}有點在意你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF5FCFE&\3c&H0080FF&}進來喝杯茶吧
